@startuml

title Policy Hydration Layer

start

* Checks TenantContext
* Checks BranchContext
* Checks ProfileContext

switch (result?)

case (valid tenant, customer profile)

:Fetches tenant-wide customer policies if branch is None
Fetches branch-wide customer policies if branch is valid;

case (valid tenant, staff profile)

:Fetches tenant-wide staff policies if branch is None
Fetches branch-wide staff policies if branch is valid;

case (admin tenant, system profile)

:Fetches platform-wide system policies;

endswitch

* Returns Option<Vec<Policy>>

if (is some?) then (yes)

* Injects PolicyContext(Some(Arc(Vec<Policy>)))

else (no)

* Injects PolicyContext(None)

endif

stop

@enduml

